WEBVTT

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:11.000
Open DataFilter and check files

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
Check the tiers to be filtered

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.500
Click on "Single" button

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:47.500
Click on "Label" button

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:58.500
Enter the text "toto" in the area of "Patterns to find:"

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Choose the appropriate function: "exact" for our example

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.500
Click "OK"

00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:09.500
The filter is in the list

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.500
Fix the name of the resulting tier

00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:16.500
Click one of the "Apply" buttons

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
New tiers are appended in the files

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:47.500
Click on "Save" or "Save All" button